A Perl tool to query packages using packages.sabayon.org.
Run it with --help to see options.

screenshot (v1.13, quiet mode): http://i.imgur.com/By5Az.png

Two console interfaces are available:
- interactive (when run with no parameters),
- non-interactive.


It can be installed the usual Perl way:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install # requires root

alternatively, you can clone the git repository or download needed files
manually and run this:

    ./querypkg.sh


dependencies on Gentoo and friends:
dev-lang/perl
dev-perl/JSON-XS
dev-perl/URI
dev-perl/libwww-perl
